                    <h4 class="txt-color-blueLight">YTD <span class="semi-bold">Budget to Actuals</span> <span class="pull-right txt-color-blueLight">102%<i style="padding-left: 10px;"  class="fa fa-arrow-circle-up"></i></span></h4>
